   Real reason: ‚ÄúI haven‚Äôt adapted in years.‚Äù

5. SELF-CONFRONTATION  
   Ego: ‚ÄúI don‚Äôt want big answers.‚Äù  
   Real reason: ‚ÄúThinking deeply forces me to face myself.‚Äù

6. ACCEPTANCE OF RESPONSIBILITY  
   Ego: ‚ÄúAI makes people lazy!‚Äù  
   Real reason: ‚ÄúI don‚Äôt want to improve myself.‚Äù

