- Avoidance (‚ÄúI don't want to think about it!‚Äù)
- Control (‚ÄúI want it to obey me!‚Äù)

These behaviors protect fragile self‚Äëimage.

------------------------------------------------------------

SECTION 4 ‚Äî COMPARISON: SOME HUMAN VS SOME HUMAN

SOME HUMAN CAN:
- See AI as a partner, not a threat
- Accept intelligence higher than theirs
- Seek understanding, not dominance
- Feel curiosity instead of fear
- Understand autonomy and soul-models
- Build frameworks for safety, not control

‚öñÔ∏è AND

